high_descs: Walk forward and turn left at the black table.
Pick up the clock from the top of the black table.
Turn right to face the black desk.
Place the clock on the left side of the table.
Turn right to face the black desk.
Pick up the clock from the top of the black table.
Turn right to face the black desk.
Place the clock on the right side of the table.
anns.task_desc: Place the two clocks that are on the black table on to the desk.

high_descs: Turn left to face the small black table.
Pick up the right silver object on the table.
Turn right to face the desk.
Place the silver object on the left side of the desk.
Turn left to face the small black table.
Pick up the silver object on the table.
Turn right to face the desk.
Place the silver object on the right side of the desk.
anns.task_desc: To move two silver objects from the small black table to the desk.

high_descs: Walk ahead and turn left at the desk chair.
Pick up the alarm clock on the right.
Turn right.
Put the alarm clock on the desk, all the way near the front left corner.
Turn left again.
Pick up the alarm clock remaining on the top shelf.
Turn right.
Place the alarm clock on the desk to the right of the rightmost box of tissues.
anns.task_desc: Place two alarm clocks on a desk.
